{"tid":923971,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Dead Redemption 2 Online(LIHKG RDR CLUB)約戰解任專區","createTime":"2018-12-01T17:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T11:28:13.000Z","uid":115042,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c62257b34a042ee2855a0b3b5bbdd255446b20c3","tid":923971,"uid":115042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:02:58.000Z","msg":"因為隊員數目佔增多,所以開個專區,方便大家交流溝通<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newsweek.com/sites/www.newsweek.com/files/styles/full/public/2018/11/06/rockstar-red-dead-redemption-2-online-beta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newsweek.com%2Fsites%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Ffull%2Fpublic%2F2018%2F11%2F06%2Frockstar-red-dead-redemption-2-online-beta.jpg&h=620def08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫會名稱:LIHKG RDR CLUB<br />\n徽記:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xH3mWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xH3mWS.png&h=14ca63c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平台: PS4<br />\n入隊網址:<a href=\"https://zh.socialclub.rockstargames.com/crew/lihkg_rdr_club/hierarchy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.socialclub.rockstargames.com%2Fcrew%2Flihkg_rdr_club%2Fhierarchy&d=wspzBABIzLxXj8IevvQA8nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ea9967f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.socialclub.rockstargames.com/crew/lihkg_rdr_club/hierarchy</a><br />\nUPDATE下消息:<br />\n1.有興趣既玩家歡迎加入,已申請入隊既請耐心等候處理<br />\n2.入咗隊既會員建議SOCIAL CLUB設定&gt;已連結的帳戶&gt;連結PSN帳戶<br />\n再係隱私權設定可見度為每個人或好友和幫會,方便互ADD<br />\n如果因私人理由唔SET就可能要自己搵其他方法ADD其他隊員<br />\n3.另我都係PSN社群開咗GROUP,都係叫LIHKG RDR CLUB,遲D我會招大家,留意PSN訊息<br />\n4.如果隊員們已經係PSN成為好友,其實可以係PSN好友到新增名單,再將隊員們加入名單中,咁就方便分類<br />\n5. TG我決定唔開了,因為唔想部手機日震夜震,當然隊員之間可以私下開,<br />\n係到講聲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6.最後希望大家用純享樂心態同其他隊員享受遊戲<br />\n一齊打下團體戰,跑下馬,幫手解下任,浪跡模式時大家互相照應<br />\n大家都可以POST下GAME相,有咩最新消息係到開心SHARE<br />\nJUST FOR FUN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4440f6f6180a549d1b9119fc9680dc536a1986a4","tid":923971,"uid":115042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HcPxfvM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHcPxfvM.jpg&h=01251b61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPOST返同其中一位巴打既合照(希望遲D影到大合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n多謝你教識我好多野同幫手解任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8870bfd4cd282fd4098efc5997c7bd6af885b2","tid":923971,"uid":8570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"申請咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea4e673854d782643c6b7f2a1df622676707554","tid":923971,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:32:38.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"fa0569f0f701cc71995a301f6f47acde02dfeeaa","tid":923971,"uid":224815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:34:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人開tg<br />\n<br />\n利申:全職獵人"},{"pid":"d5314550968609300c006b1ef34119c3e5e25542","tid":923971,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"快開TG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b7902090dab84282483f0911e7f4eca42224d9","tid":923971,"uid":204644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:41:36.000Z","msg":"入左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494a705b560fcd2f4a85484b98712e4f6e553fd7","tid":923971,"uid":204644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa0569f0f701cc71995a301f6f47acde02dfeeaa","tid":923971,"uid":224815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:34:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人開tg<br />\n<br />\n利申:全職獵人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:42:27.000Z","ms